# Introduction {#intro}

```{r}
library(car)
library(compute.es)
library(effects)
library(ggplot2)
library(multcomp)
library(pastecs)
library(WRS2)
library(tidyverse)
```

## Import data

Import tick data

```{r}
tick <- read.csv("./data/tickdata.csv",header=T)
glimpse(tick)
```

### Raw data table

```{r}
kableExtra::kable(head(tick))
```

### Plot raw data

```{r}
plot(x = tick$HLL,
     y = tick$Max_2m,
     col = tick$Yes1N0,
     pch = 5,
     xlab = "HLL"
     ,ylab = "m/s")
```
